column1: Baby Barnaby's//// I ordered the green eggs with a biscuit instead of toast from the guy next to me's recommendation.   It was great
column2: although very very cheesy.  The biscuits are good too
column3: not the real crumbly kind and they kind of taste like honey.  It also comes with a nice pile of breakfast potatoes
column4: crunchy on the outside like fries.
